title: Easy Chicken Biryani | Maunika Gowardhan
description:
Maunika really has created a show stopper of a dish with her Easy Chicken Biryani recipe.  Chicken thighs in a spicy yogurt marinade cooked with fresh tomatoes and layered with Basmati rice, saffron infused milk and garam masala.  Delicious.

And for more incredible Indian recipes make sure you check out Maunika’s website - http://maunikagowardhan.co.uk/

For a mango and saffron lassi check out Maunika’s delicious recipe over on Drinks Tube http://jamieol.com/mangosaffronlassi
